      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BLACKBRUSH BEN (1) has an honest record despite remaining a maiden after 11 starts. Hit the frame again last start finishing third (16.52) at Launceston. Can go on with it. JET SPRINT (2) filled a minor placing last start at this track behind Longhorn (19.86) in a Grade 6. Must be included in calculations. BUCKLE UP MOONIE (8) was checked in the run and safely held when sixth (16.56) in a Grade 6 over 278m at Launceston. Key chance on best form. BORN CRANKY (5) is a Jillian Stamford-trained newcomer by Aston Rupee out of Leica Prayer. No favours with the draw and will need to begin well. Can sneak into the frame with the right run.",
